\c 13
\s Murairo wematangwe
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi achiti:
\v 2 Ndiitirei mutsvene dangwe rose, rinozarura chizvaro chimwe nechimwe pakati pevana vaIsraeri, remunhu nerechipfuwo, nderangu\x + 13.12,13,15; 34.19. Num.. 8.16; 18.15,17. 22.29,30. Rev. 27.26. Num.. 3.13; 8.16,17. Det. 15.19. Eze. 44.30. Ruk. 2.23.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Zvino Mozisi wakati kuvanhu: Rangarirai zuva rino ramakabuda naro muEgipita, kubva muimba yeuranda\x + 12.42. Det. 16.3.\x*; nokuti nesimba reruoko Jehovha wakakubudisirai pano. Zvino ngakurege kudyiwa chingwa chakaviriswa\x + 12.8.\x*.
\v 4 Nezuva rino munobuda mumwedzi waAbhibhi\x + 12.2. Neh. 2.1. Esi. 3.7.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Zvino zvichava Jehovha paachakupinza munyika yeVaKenani neVaHiti neVaAmori neVaHivhi neVaJebhusi\x + 3.8,17; 23.23; 33.2; 34.11. Det. 7.1; 20.17. Josh. 3.10; 12.8; 24.11. Vato. 3.5. Gen.. 15.19,20.\x* yaakapikira kumadzibaba ako kukupa\x + 13.11; 6.8.\x*, nyika inoyerera mukaka neuchi\x + 3.8.\x*, kuti uchachengetedza shumiro iyi nemwedzi uno\x + 12.25,26.\x*.
\v 6 Mazuva manomwe uchadya chingwa chisina kuviriswa; uye muzuva rechinomwe achava mabiko kuna Jehovha\x + 12.15,16.\x*.
\v 7 Chingwa chisina kuviriswa chichadyiwa mazuva manomwe; uye hakungaonekwi chakaviriswa kwauri; hongu, mbiriso haingaonekwi kwauri pamiganhu yako yose.
\p
\v 8 Zvino uchaudza mwanakomana wako nezuva iro uchiti: Nekuda kweizvo Jehovha zvaakaita kwandiri pandakabuda muEgipita\x + 13.14; 12.26.\x*.
\v 9 Zvino chichava kwauri chiratidzo paruoko rwako\x + 13.16. Det. 6.8; 11.18. Num.. 15.39. Mat. 23.5.\x*, nechirangaridzo\x + 12.14.\x* pakati pemeso ako, kuti murairo waJehovha uve mumuromo mako; nokuti neruoko rune simba Jehovha wakakubudisa paEgipita.
\v 10 Naizvozvo uchachengeta chimiso ichi nenguva yacho yakatarwa gore negore\x + 12.14,17,24,43.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Zvino zvichava kana Jehovha akupinza kunyika yeVaKenani, sezvaakakupikira iwe nekumadzibaba ako, kuti achaipa kwauri,
\v 12 kuti uchapfuudzira kuna Jehovha chose chinozarura chizvaro, nechekutanga chose chibereko chezvipfuwo zvaunazvo; mikono ichava yaJehovha\x + 13.2.\x*.
\v 13 Nechekutanga chose chembongoro uchachidzikunura negwayana\x + 34.20.\x*; uye kana usingachidzikunuri, zvino uchavhuna mutsipa wacho; nematangwe ose evanhu pakati pevanakomana vako uchadzikunura\x + Num.. 3.46,47; 18.15,16.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Zvino zvichava kana mwanakomana wako akakubvunza munguva inouya achiti: Chii ichi\x + 12.26.\x*? kuti uchati kwaari: Nesimba reruoko Jehovha wakatibudisa kubva muEgipita, kubva paimba yeuranda\x + 13.3,16.\x*.
\v 15 Zvino zvakaitika Farao achiomesa kuti tiende, kuti Jehovha wakauraya dangwe rimwe nerimwe munyika yeEgipita\x + 12.29.\x*, kubva kudangwe remunhu kusvika kudangwe rechipfuwo; naizvozvo ndinobaira kuna Jehovha chose chinozarura chizvaro, iri mikono; asi matangwe ose evanakomana vangu ndinodzikunura\x + 13.13.\x*.
\v 16 Zvino chichava chiratidzo pamusoro peruoko rwako nevundanyara pakati pemeso ako\x + 13.9.\x*; nokuti nesimba reruoko Jehovha wakatibudisa kubva muEgipita.
\s VaIsraeri vanofamba kuenda kugungwa
\p
\v 17 Zvino zvakaitika Farao arega vanhu vaenda, kuti Mwari haana kuvatungamirira \add ne\add*nzira yenyika yeVaFirisitia, kunyange yaiva pedo; nokuti Mwari wakati: Zvimwe vanhu vangazvidemba, kana vachiona hondo, vakadzokera kuEgipita\x + 14.11,12. Num.. 14.1-4.\x*.
\v 18 Asi Mwari wakapoteredza vanhu \add ne\add*nzira yerenje reGungwa Dzvuku\x + 14.2.\x*. Zvino vana vaIsraeri vakakwira vachibva munyika yeEgipita vakashonga nhumbi dzekurwa.
\v 19 Mozisi ndokutora mapfupa aJosefa kuenda nawo; nokuti waiva apikisa zvirokwazvo vana vaIsraeri achiti: Zvirokwazvo Mwari achakushanyirai; uye muchakwira nemapfupa angu kubva pano\x + Gen.. 50.25. Josh. 24.32. Mab. 7.16.\x*.
\p
\v 20 Zvino vakasimuka kubva paSukoti, ndokuvaka misasa paEtamu, pamucheto werenje\x + 12.37. Num.. 33.6.\x*.
\v 21 Jehovha ndokuvatungamirira pamasikati mushongwe yegore kuvatungamirira munzira, uye pausiku mushongwe yemoto kuvavhenekera\x + 14.19,24; 40.38. Num.. 9.15; 10.34; 14.14. Det. 1.33. Neh. 9.12,19. Map. 78.14; 99.7; 105.39. Isa. 4.5. 1 VaKori. 10.1.\x*, kuti vafambe masikati neusiku.
\v 22 Haana kubvisa shongwe yegore pamasikati uye shongwe yemoto pausiku pamberi pevanhu.